{"tid":1467460,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今晚，大家一定要反省呢三樣嘢！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:05.000Z","uid":171302,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85bcd6d4305a8c7bb8ceba1dd63428a715609901","tid":1467460,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"經過今晚，大家一定要反省呢三樣嘢！<br />\n機場只可以文宣！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1。機場係「和你飛」，並唔係「阻你飛」。</span></span><br />\n阻住外國遊客入禁區根本就冇意思，<br />\n佢哋咁燥根本就唔會聽你講嘢。<br />\n相反只會令佢哋覺得你哋好反感，一傳十十傳百咁就玩完。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住我哋第一日係兩個月以來，贏得最漂亮嘅一仗！</span><br />\n外國遊客係我哋迫政府嘅人質，所以我哋一定要對人質好d！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2。機場最大缺點係交通配套唔夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家機場嘅交通配套根本就係不勝負荷。<br />\n大家記住，你要入機場食飯，只要每日打爆佢個交通配套，自然所有航班就會cancel！<br />\n<br />\n大家入去食飯根本就唔會<span style=\"color: red;\">俾人拉，俾人打，食催淚彈</span>，最安全！又比到壓力政府！！<br />\n目標為本，只要cancel 哂90%航班，咁就任務完成！<br />\n只要佢哋仲有少少航班升降上落，根本就唔會出催淚彈！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3。鬼，點都捉唔晒</span></span><br />\n講真俾你捉到隻鬼又點？入面咁多鬼係入面你點捉？好似今晚咁，比你捉到兩隻，但外國遊客個Focus就會錯晒！大家要識得分輕重！記得大家初心係乜嘢？<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">同意嘅請幫手推post</span></strong><br />\n有錯都可以指正"},{"pid":"0380bd4578013e2f8a11f8b58cb282dbe989fee3","tid":1467460,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa85a14651cb9debc26cdb14a9b0bda1d78c2f96","tid":1467460,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0380bd4578013e2f8a11f8b58cb282dbe989fee3","tid":1467460,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"